subtitleNullable: Involves sales rep interaction with customers alongwith sales pipeline
descriptionNullable:
### Context

A company has many products and several customers. Using data provided forecast the sales between different dates.

### Content
Dataset contains two files:
First has interactions between the sales representative and the customer company in raw text form, these are computer generated but can provide insight on how the sales are affected by the behaviour.
Second has the sales-pipeline representing various details about the sale opportunity whether it was closed or not and the days in which it was closed.


### Inspiration
Feel free to tweak the data and get better results.All the best.
